divs: Sighting Detailsat 9pm saw lights north of hwy377 and cr 279 at our angle we could see a dark outline of the craft which was large and circular in shape, it was smaller than the one we watch for 20 min. back 3 years ago, 10 min later saw light toward dublin texas. Lots of jets with strob light flashing in a spread out formation wing to wing followed 5 min later like they were searching for something. same as last time but quicker and more of them. I seemed like alot of private planes were in the area also this time. we actually saw the craft this time. Probably a government plasma test.
